(8627, 434, 8441, 'Glxspk', 173, '', 1237755502, 'It cycles faster than a Beretta thats for sure and is wicked with doubles at Skeet.\n\nI''ve only had a malfunction once where it didn''t chamber the last shell while at skeet but you have to understand that I was using weaker loads and had shot more than 300 shells, I had not cleaned it so it had residue from my past escapades...\n\nFor the brevity of it: No jams no other malfunctions. A very good weapon indeed. \n\nI had two and had put one on sale with Hannan at DAAD after my resolution to get rid of surplus. \n\nFeel free to contact him.', 0, 1, '115.186.68.162', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 569, 10476),
